  <div class="row ">
	  <div class="widecolumn">
	  			<div class="action_text purple_border" id="strength1">
			<h1>Our depth of experience and network of thought leaders</h1>		
			<p>We have over 20 years experience exploring and developing approaches to responsible and responsive governance and public sector leadership in Canada and abroad. Our primary goal is to promote and share good practices, through <a href="http://iog.ca/research">research</a>, <a href="http://iog.ca/advisory">advisory services</a> and <a href="http://iog.ca/learning">learning products</a>. <a href="http://iog.ca/about-us">Learn more about our team</a>.</p>
			</div>
	  			<div class="action_text green_border" id="strength2">
			<h1>A safe space for discussion and sharing of ideas</h1>		
			<p>Our <a title="Executive Leadership Program" href="http://iog.ca/learning/executive-leadership-program">Executive Leadership Program</a>, <a title="Leadership boot camps" href="http://iog.ca/learning/leadership-boot-camps">leadership boot camps</a>, <a title="Courses" href="http://iog.ca/learning/courses">day courses</a>, and <a href="http://iog.ca/learning/custom-courses">custom courses</a> are designed to be safe spaces for dialogue and sharing ideas. They are informed by our <a href="http://iog.ca/research">research</a> and <a href="http://iog.ca/advisory">advisory services</a>, and developed, tested and taught by former senior public servants. <a title="Learning" href="http://iog.ca/learning">Learn more about learning opportunities at the IOG</a>.</p>
			</div>
	  			<div class="action_text blue_border" id="strength3">
			<h1>Our business driven and practical approach </h1>		
			<p>We recognize the importance of connecting vision to strategy in a way that aligns internal service delivery with the evolving expectations of citizens. We bring both the first hand knowledge and passion required to improve the way public services are delivered to and accessed by citizens. <a title="About Us" href="http://iog.ca/about-us/">Learn more about us.</a></p>
			</div>
